n- Payment、Shipping、Email等服务调用都出现3-4.6倍的延迟增长\n\n### 3. **次要影响 - cartservice**\n- cartservice也出现4.2倍延迟，但相对productcatalogservice的影响较小\n\n**根因定位**：基于调用链拓扑分析，productcatalogservice是最下游的异常服务，其严重延迟导致上游frontend和checkoutservice出现连锁反应。这符合\"寻找最下游异常\"的根因定位原则。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "tidb-tikv is the root cause due to severe storage performance degradation (region_pending dropped 73.8%, io_util p99 increased 658.7%, cpu_usage p99 increased 126.8%)"}
